{"tid":1466992,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［重開］ 各位手足入一入嚟 一齊諗下下一步點做","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:01:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T18:02:04.000Z","uid":46239,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e6f088c5a5e85cc7fc4844db07887af5f67de59c","tid":1466992,"uid":46239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:01:56.000Z","msg":"今日機場一役 的確有好多做得唔好嘅地方<br />\n但係就算做成點 都係我地手足<br />\n有咩事 就一齊補鑊<br />\n今日 小弟都有份放工就去機場坐 <br />\n在場的確有好多外國人喊曬咁 好想返屋企<br />\n佢地可能已經冇曬錢<br />\n亦都搵唔到地方住<br />\n始終香港對於佢地嚟講唔係佢地嘅家<br />\n所以我個人認為 癱瘓機場要停一停<br />\n<br />\n反思完<br />\n就要補鑊啦<br />\n聽日如果各位巴絲得閒嘅<br />\n可以入一入機場幫下各位受影響嘅外國人手<br />\n要俾人知道<br />\n我地雖然早兩日阻住到佢地<br />\n但我地對準嘅<br />\n係而家林鄭呢個政權<br />\n<br />\n同埋記住<br />\nBe humble Be water"},{"pid":"fe1d84aa08e000a2909e89091a33f183dcc4a106","tid":1466992,"uid":46239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:03:45.000Z","msg":"麻煩停止捉鬼<br />\n疑心引致分化"},{"pid":"56169f0cade1832d878b9d777d51c3e719ad438f","tid":1466992,"uid":46239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:05:12.000Z","msg":"各位手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adf1e8fb42d92a9b7623b018ba6522448cab5240","tid":1466992,"uid":46239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:10:47.000Z","msg":"唔好再捉鬼啦"},{"pid":"eac7081a96ca0b7448ee1aab61bb42d111fd13d9","tid":1466992,"uid":297071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:11:28.000Z","msg":"【安心又偷食】仲有冇人記得許志安，黃心穎？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1466951\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1466951</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"49cda8c57838bb7d59c2b89aa213559a470a9ba2","tid":1466992,"uid":268860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:12:56.000Z","msg":"隔日做？"},{"pid":"98d6b6e6c2131e96db4518ad5c1023c6674d822b","tid":1466992,"uid":46239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49cda8c57838bb7d59c2b89aa213559a470a9